         <abstract id="aspace_c25aba272bcb1a66eaf247828f51ec8e">The notebooks contain Orcutt's notes from medical school courses including physiology courses by Russell Chittenden and Yandell Henderson, pathology, bacteriology, pharmacology,  histology, therapeutics by Oliver T. Osborne, and clinics by George Blumer and Wilder Tileston.  The histology notes contain illustrations colored in pencil.  The bacteriology notes are in an illustrated notebook printed especially for the bacteriology course at Yale.  The physiology notes contain tracings from a kymograph or similar device.</abstract>
